    <item>
      <title>Cherry on Top</title>
      <link>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/cherry-on-top/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2018 11:57:50 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/cherry-on-top/</guid>
      <description>
&lt;ul class=&#34;ingredients&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;6 fresh cherries, pitted&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;1½ oz vodka&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;½ oz Luxardo Maraschino&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;¾ oz lemon juice&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;¼ oz simple syrup&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;div class=&#34;instructions e-instructions&#34;&gt;
  Muddle five cherries in the bottom of your cocktail shaker. Add the liquids and ice. Shake.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/techniques/straining/#double-straining&#34;&gt;Double strain&lt;/a&gt; into a Collins glass filled with ice. Set a cherry atop the ice as a garnish.
&lt;/div&gt;


</description>
